4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:16,000
You need to rest.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,000
You're right, I do.

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,142
Look, Jesse, wherever you guys go next, give him some time

7
00:00:22,142 --> 00:00:24,000
